Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Ten Hundred Miles 一千里遠
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我在準備放手，讓他們接手\NI'm letting it go, and letting them in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}正思考著要怎麼重起\Npondering for a way to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}乾乾淨淨，俐俐落落\Ncoming out clean, cleaning up nice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我在準備改變，讓他們幫我\NThey're shaping me up and taking me in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}撫平傷痛並帶我向前\Nforgiving my pain and riding the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}是否回家就會改變一切\NWill everything change when we arrive?
Comment: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,## 導歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}星群墜落，前所未有的快\NThe stars are falling faster than before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}月亮招喚，但地球招更猛\NThe moon is calling, but earth is calling more
Comment: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)}喔哦，噢\NWhoa, ohhh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}現在是否看清？\Nnow can't ya see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)}喔哦，噢\NWhoa, ohhh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}自由真是清新\Nso good to be free
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)}喔哦\NWhoa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我不需要任何東西\NI don't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)}因為我就—\Nbecause I'm just,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}—就已經是我自己\NI'm just who I want to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就是自己\NI'm just me
Comment: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在太空中，是真的孤獨\NIt's terribly lonely out in space
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}很少笑聲，笑容抹滅\Nlaughter is rare, and smiles erased
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}朋友消失，噢，我是怎樣？\Nfriendship is gone; oh, what had I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但，我學到教訓，不會跑掉\NBut, now that I've learned, I'll stay for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我已經飛了一千里遠\Nnow that I've burned ten-hundred miles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我不會再來，不怎麼好玩\NI'll never go back, it wasn't much fun
Comment: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,## 導歌
